<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - FarmFresh</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <%- include('partials/flash') %>

    <div class="about-container">
        <header class="about-hero">
            <div class="about-hero-content">
                <h1 class="about-hero-title">Connecting Communities, One Harvest at a Time</h1>
                <p class="about-hero-subtitle">We believe in the power of fresh, local food to bring people together and build a healthier future.</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="about-main">
            <section class="about-section about-mission">
                <div class="mission-image">
                    <img src="/assets/images/farmerpic.jpg" alt="Lush green farm field">
                </div>
                <div class="mission-text">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>Our mission is to bridge the gap between local farmers and consumers. We empower farmers by giving them a platform to sell their produce directly, ensuring they receive a fair price for their hard work. For consumers, we provide convenient access to the freshest, most nutritious food available, straight from the source.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="about-section how-it-works">
                <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
                <div class="steps-grid">
                    <div class="step-card">
                        <div class="step-icon">①</div>
                        <h3>Discover Farmers</h3>
                        <p>Browse profiles of local farmers in your area and learn about their practices and products.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-card">
                        <div class="step-icon">②</div>
                        <h3>Shop Fresh</h3>
                        <p>Fill your cart with fresh fruits, vegetables, dairy, and more, all listed directly by the farmers.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-card">
                        <div class="step-icon">③</div>
                        <h3>Get It Delivered</h3>
                        <p>Enjoy convenient, contactless delivery straight to your doorstep, bringing the farm to you.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="about-section cta-section">
                <h2>Join the Movement</h2>
                <p>Whether you're a farmer looking to grow your business or a consumer seeking healthier food, you have a place at FarmFresh.</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">Start Shopping</a>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-secondary">Join as a Farmer</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>